title: The Winds of Winter (excerpts) - George R. R. Martin
description:
A collection of all the officially released completed chapters of George R. R. Martin's upcoming book, The Winds of Winter, book five of the A Song of Ice and Fire series. Included are the following chapters:

- THEON I
- ARIANNE I
- BARRISTAN I
- TYRION II
- MERCY
- ALAYNE I

Compiled using source image and style files from the A Dance with Dragons ebook to give it a polished feel, using text from official sources such as on George R. R. Martin's own various websites, this ebook is uploaded in the following formats:

- EPUB
- MOBI

Cover art used courtesy DeviantArt user nateblunt.

Don't forget to purchase the actual book in the event that it actually gets released in the next half century! ;)
